'''Mohamed Amine Ben Hamida''' ({{langx|ar|محمد أمين بن حميدة}}; born 15 December 1995) is a Tunisian [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|left back]] for {{Tunisian football updater|EST}} club [[Espérance Sportive de Tunis|Espérance de Tunis]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].<ref>[https://www.goalzz.com/?player=125454/ goalzz.com]</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mohamed Amine Ben Hamida - Soccer player profile & career statistics - Global Sports Archive|url=https://globalsportsarchive.com/people/soccer/mohamed-amine-ben-hamida/382119/|access-date=2022-01-28|website=globalsportsarchive.com}}</ref><ref name="sports.yahoo.com">{{Cite web|title=Mohamed Amine Ben Hmida {{!}} Tunisia {{!}} Stats {{!}} News {{!}} Profile - Yahoo Sports|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/soccer/players/1942736/|access-date=2022-01-28|website=sports.yahoo.com|language=en-US}}</ref>

==Club career==
His contract with Espérance de Tunis runs till 30 June 2026.<ref name=":0" /> In 2017, he was transferred from Espérance de Tunis to Avenir de Soliman. Avenir de Soliman received Mohamed Amine Ben Hamida from Espérance de Tunis on a free loan.<ref name=":0" />

==International career==
He made his debut for the [[Tunisia national football team]] on 30 November 2021 in a [[2021 FIFA Arab Cup]] game against [[Mauritania national football team|Mauritania]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FIFA]]|url=https://www.fifa.com/tournaments/mens/arabcup/arabcup2021/match-center/400175814|title=Tunisia v Mauritania game report|date=30 November 2021|accessdate=28 January 2022}}</ref>

==Style of play==
Left is his favoured foot.<ref name="sports.yahoo.com"/> Mohamed Amine Ben Hamida has also been deployed as a wing back and an inverted [[Defender (association football)|wing back]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Mohamed Amine Ben Hamida {{!}} FootballTransfers.com|url=https://www.footballtransfers.com/en/players/amine-ben-hamida|access-date=2022-01-28|website=www.footballtransfers.com|language=en}}</ref>

